notes.note:
Good morning,
            i would like to update you on the results of the TSB on the terrain in question.
            i have attached images of our findings
                    upon inspection of the valve cover we found a few litres of water accumulation within , and upon removal found a murky mix of contaminated oil. As per the TSB it will require a valve cover replacement. The valve cover replacement kit comes with the appropriate gaskets. We will then drill out the recommended hole in the plenum valley on the intake manifold and change the oil. At the same time we will need to clean out the intake manifold and plenum chambers, as well as replacing the lower intake manifold gasket.

the pricing and part numbers are as follows:

        Valve cover kit - part #82760801
        $348.12
        replacement labor - 1.4hrs - $182.00

        intake manifold lower gasket - part # MS97208
        $56.97
        labor for removal, cleaning and re installation - 2.3 hours - $ 299.00
       
        Oil and filter replacement - $93.45
notes.content:
Good morning,
i would like to update you on the results of the TSB on the terrain in question.
i have attached images of our findings
upon inspection of the valve cover we found a few litres of water accumulation within , and upon removal found a murky mix of contaminated oil. As per the TSB it will require a valve cover replacement. The valve cover replacement kit comes with the appropriate gaskets. We will then drill out the recommended hole in the plenum valley on the intake manifold and change the oil. At the same time we will need to clean out the intake manifold and plenum chambers, as well as replacing the lower intake manifold gasket.

the pricing and part numbers are as follows:

Valve cover kit - part #82760801
$348.12
replacement labor - 1.4hrs - $182.00

intake manifold lower gasket - part # MS97208
$56.97
labor for removal, cleaning and re installation - 2.3 hours - $ 299.00

Oil and filter replacement - $93.45
